# Prisma & Database

- Single source of truth: `prisma/schema.prisma`; migrations committed, never edit prod DB manually.
- Use transactions for order + inventory decrement + payment record.

```typescript
// GOOD: atomic order placement
await prisma.$transaction(async (tx) => {
  await tx.inventory.updateMany({ where: { sku, qty: { gte: 1 } }, data: { qty: { decrement: 1 } } });
  return tx.order.create({ data: orderData });
});
```

- Index foreign keys and filters: `teamId`, `league`, `status`, `createdAt`.
- Soft-delete customers (`deletedAt`) for LFPDPPP retention policies; hard-delete only after legal hold clears.
- Seed realistic LMB/MLB sample data in `prisma/seed.ts`; no production PII in seeds.
